items.name: Fully-SCNN
items.description: An example of SC-FCNN on MNIST. This work is an un-offical implementation of paper: Dynamic Energy-Accuracy Trade-off Using Stochastic Computing in Deep Neural Networks. We use full-SC process, all values are representated as bit-stream. and got result acc = 97.2%.
